        "TileImage": "$($repository 856b2aa2-e224-48c3-b890-01fdf4dba6de).Image",
        "Description": "Find the secrets of Whittleton Creek and eliminate the evil that hides among us. There&apos;s rumours of a muffin maker with a shady secret ingredient, a corrupt politician, a plumber who&apos;s company is being audited by the IRS for potential laundering, an unscrupulous nurse who&apos;s patients reguarly overdose, and a mailman who mysteriously connects all of these nefarious people. \r\rOnly you 47 can bring this quaint town back into peace.\r\rI&apos;ll leave you to prepare.",
